      "writtenOn": "2020-11-16T15:26:38Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "The main difference AFAIU is inherited props cascade down, while non-inherited props are only pulled from the immediate parent when \"inherit\" is specified.\n\ne.g.\n\n  \u003cg opacity\u003d\"50%\"\u003e\n    \u003crect opacity\u003d\"inherit\"/\u003e\n  \u003c/g\u003e\n\napplies .5 opacity twice, while\n\n  \u003cg opacity\u003d\"50%\"\u003e\n    \u003cg\u003e\n      \u003crect opacity\u003d\"inherit\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/g\u003e\n  \u003c/g\u003e\n\nonly applies .5 opacity once.",
      "revId": "b856aef4f02af477a42f657716c9674718d50317",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02"
    },
    {
      "unresolved": true,
      "key": {
