      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-11-16T16:24:28Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "That example makes sense to me (pull from immediate parent when \"inherit\" is specified). See other comment for discussion on when exactly that \"pull\" should happen.",
      "parentUuid": "0c5df704_228ae6da",
      "revId": "b856aef4f02af477a42f657716c9674718d50317",
